ate id=\"B:0\"></template><main class=\"relative z-[3] mx-auto w-full max-w-[860px] px-[22px] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\"></main><!--/$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"relative z-[3] flex justify-center px-[22px] pt-[30px] pb-11\"><div class=\"flex w-full max-w-[1180px] flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-[18px] sm:px-[22px]\" style=\"border-radius:20px;background:var(--glass-bg);background-image:var(--glass-tint);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur)) saturate(180%);border:1px solid var(--glass-brd);box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 var(--glass-hi)\"><span class=\"text-[13px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">© 2026 Daffa Ilham Restupratama</span><span class=\"mono text-[11px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Data · Business · Finance · Maps · Walking Tours</span></div></footer></div><script>requestAnimationFrame(function(){$RT=performance.now()});</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0a1gboz92241g.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><div hidden id=\"S:0\"><main class=\"relative z-[3] mx-auto w-full max-w-[860px] px-[22px] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\"><a class=\"mono inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[12.5px] transition-colors hover:text-(--accent-ink)\" style=\"color:var(--ink-dim)\" href=\"/tours\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"transform:rotate(180deg)\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg>All tours</a><h1 class=\"mt-5 font-bold\" style=\"font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.03em\">Bogor Waterfall Nature Trip</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-[16px]\" style=\"line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-dim)\">A nature-focused trip to waterfall areas around Bogor, designed for visitors who want a refreshing escape from the city.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-[7px]\"><span class=\"chip rounded-full px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 7 12 12 15 14\"></polyline></svg>Half day to full day</span><span class=\"chip rounded-full px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>Bogor Station or agreed meeting point.</span></div><div role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Bogor Waterfall Nature Trip cover\" class=\"mt-6 aspect-[16/9] w-full\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(150deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--green) 30%, var(--surface)), color-mix(in srgb, var(--teal) 24%, var(--surface)));border-radius:15px\"></div><section><h2 class=\"mt-10 mb-3 text-[22px] font-bold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.02em\">About this tour</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">This tour is a flexible nature trip focused on waterfall destinations around Bogor. The route depends on weather, accessibility, transport options, and visitor fitness level. It is best for small groups who are comfortable with outdoor conditions and possible route changes.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mt-10 mb-3 text-[22px] font-bold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.02em\">Good to know</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-6 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-semibold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.01em\">Suitable for</h3><ul class=\"mt-2.5 flex flex-col gap-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>nature lovers</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>small groups</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>outdoor beginners</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>city escape travelers</li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-semibold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.01em\">Not suitable for</h3><ul class=\"mt-2.5 flex flex-col gap-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--ink-faint)\"></span>visitors with mobility limitations</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--ink-faint)\"></span>travelers who dislike wet or muddy paths</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--ink-faint)\"></span>visitors expecting luxury facilities</li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-semibold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.01em\">What to prepare</h3><ul class=\"mt-2.5 flex flex-col gap-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>comfortable outdoor sandals or shoes</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>change of clothes</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>waterproof bag</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>water bottle</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>cash</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>rain protection</li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-semibold\" style=\"letter-spacing:-0.01em\">Included</h3><ul class=\"mt-2.5 flex flex-col gap-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>route planning</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" style=\"line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-dim)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mt-[7px] h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>basic trip guidance</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[14px]\" styl